<br>
Since I got POP (about 3 weeks after the release), I have gotten in 2 (two, zwei, dos) groups that were complete strangers.<br>
<br>
The only times I am ever able to get a group is with guildies or people that I raid with.<br>
<br>
Thank God I can two box and use my cleric to CH the pet.  Or I'd have quit the mage already.<br>
<br>
I keep LFG flag on go from planes to planes shouting for groups, never get asked to join.  One day I spent 1.5 hours LFG going from POJ, to POD, to PON, to POI, spending about 15-20 mins in each zone while shouting lfg in POT when running between the zones.<br>
<br>
The cleric is lvl 53 and if I don't have him on roleplay and AFK, he'll get on average 5 tells in 7 mins to join a group somewhere.  Its sick.<br>
<br>
Mage?  Notta.  On the plus side, ME had a whopping 5 people there at 9pm CST last night.  Think I found me a soloin spot till 60.<br>
<br>
